v=2+1
print"Vnow equals itself plus one, make it worth",v
v=52
print"v can store any numerical value, to be used elsewhere",v
print"for examle, in a sentence, V is now worth", v
print"v times 5 equals",v*5
print"but v still nly remains",v
print"to make v five times bigger, you would have to type v=v*5"
v=v*5
print"there you go, now v equals", v, "and not", v/5
